sub_title: Senior Finance Analyst at Booking.com, MSc.
summary:
Sevgi Ozdemir is a senior finance analyst at Booking.com, currently lives and works in the Netherlands. 

Prior to Booking.com, she worked at Amazon in Luxembourg and Nestle in Istanbul. She has experience in FX hedging, forecasting, cost controlling, budgeting, and company acquisition. 

She holds a Master of Science degree from Sabanci Business School in Finance and Bachelor of Science degree from Middle East Technical University in Business Administration. She is the first and only 3-year graduate of METU BA. 

She is a feminist, LGBTQ+ ally and animal rights advocate.
